{"tid":925704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[時事台 Yes IT]  Too Long 唔使 Read，聽就得喇","createTime":"2018-12-03T02:41:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T04:28:51.000Z","uid":54824,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d464be05a7010a6530afcc838dab720aa5c52dd0","tid":925704,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:41:36.000Z","msg":"時事台好多巴絲打都會貼一啲有質素嘅文章。但係好多人一句too long didn't read 再話唔睇。 <br />\n<br />\n明白有時睇文章真係好嘥精神，又唔可以分心去做其他嘢。<br />\n<br />\n我而家就介紹呢一個text-to-speech嘅app工具，佢可以讀啲長文章出嚟，你用耳聽就得啦。可以邊聽邊做其他嘢，當聽電台節目咁樣。佢可以讀粵語英文。好易用。<br />\n<br />\n 先裝呢個app<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBPEQ9N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBPEQ9N.png&h=91e87fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 有長文章想聽，就選擇曬所有字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SwUA8RX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSwUA8RX.png&h=a6938020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選擇「分享」然之後「朗讀」咁就得了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0b2CCMX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0b2CCMX.png&h=8671f092&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXkwHdL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXkwHdL.png&h=88018e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有啲舊android機冇裝到google嘅語音輸出，只要裝返就得。你哋睇下有冇下面嘅「粵語」部件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTFMv7E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTFMv7E.png&h=fb96d2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGzxrGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGzxrGX.png&h=45dd07e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af5e586b0d440cac2165ce17e8ad1b8ad49c1bbf","tid":925704,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"太多掣要撳 唔用"},{"pid":"32041b0c3c9e68f4058c6a90d612bc149c9b55b8","tid":925704,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:16:48.000Z","msg":"用google tts都要限粵語英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ecb8970f36cd11c772c47b6166929c27acb397","tid":925704,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af5e586b0d440cac2165ce17e8ad1b8ad49c1bbf","tid":925704,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T02:56:14.000Z","msg":"太多掣要撳 唔用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"咁好 lu <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96862352e9f9492a02f7ed9bd2349e791faa9cef","tid":925704,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"Too different no use <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}